<A>__{attendants poke around underneath a bed and pull out a very old trembling vegetable. other attendants wrap an old dead lunatic with no teeth and foam on his open lips into a dirty sheet and haul him away. billy amid the lunatics. we move closer and closer to him, the head count regressing. the room has become a torture cell the noise louder, louder, closing in on billy.}
